# Diabetes Prediction ML System 🏥

**Production-ready machine learning pipeline** that predicts diabetes from medical data.

## 📊 Quick Stats

- **Dataset**: 768 patient records
- **Classes**: 65% No Diabetes, 35% Diabetes (imbalanced)
- **Best Model**: XGBoost
- **F1-Score**: 0.71 (handles class imbalance)
- **Deployment**: Docker + Flask API

## 🚀 Quick Start (30 seconds)

### Option 1: Local Python
\`\`\`bash
